original_title: Stewart Francis - Outstanding in His Field
overview: Live from London’s Hammersmith Apollo, this specially-filmed performance of the 2012 stand-up show from killer-gag purveyor, Stewart Francis, features a brand new crop of brilliant one liners and wisecracks – including the gag that won the funniest joke award at the 2012 Edinburgh Fringe.
title: Stewart Francis - Outstanding in His Field
